Employee structure and change As of September 30, 2023, Siemens employed 320,000

people around the world. This amounts to an increase of about 9,000 employees from September 30, 2022. 55% of our employees were based in Europe, the Commonwealth of Independent States (C.I.S.), the Middle East, and Africa, 24% in Asia and Australia, and 21% in North America, Central America, and South America.

